casebody.data:
The State ex rel. White, Pros. Atty., Appellee, v. Billings, Appellant, et al.

[Cite as State ex rel. White v. Billings, 117 Ohio St.3d 536, 2OO8-Ohio-1590.]

(No. 2007-1839 Submitted March 12, 2008 Decided April 9, 2008.)

{¶ 1} The judgment of the court of appeals is reversed on the authority of Hyle v. Porter, 117 Ohio St.3d 165, 2008-Ohio-542, 882 N.E.2d 899.

*537Donald W. White, Clermont County Prosecuting Attorney, and David H. Hoffmann, Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellee. Ohio Justice & Policy Center and David A. Singleton, for appellant. Moyer, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur. O’Donnell, J., dissents.
